{"word":"μεθάλλομαι","slug":"μεθάλλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεθάλλομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <a href='S:syncopated'>syncop.</a> aor2 <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>μετάλμενος</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to leap</i> or <i>rush upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to rush after</i>, in a race, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}